,"s":247.52,"e":248.34,"line":36},{"w":"the","s":248.34,"e":248.74,"line":36},{"w":"abyss","s":248.74,"e":249.24,"line":36},{"w":"sings","s":249.24,"e":249.66,"line":36},{"w":"loud","s":249.66,"e":250.14,"line":36},{"w":"Atlantis","s":252.04,"e":252.86,"line":37},{"w":"rise","s":252.86,"e":253.32,"line":37},{"w":"now","s":253.32,"e":254.48,"line":37},{"w":"Atlantis","s":255.64,"e":256.46,"line":38},{"w":"rise","s":256.46,"e":256.96,"line":38},{"w":"now","s":256.96,"e":257.37,"line":38},{"w":"Atlantis","s":266.22,"e":267.62,"line":39},{"w":"rise","s":267.62,"e":267.62,"line":39},{"w":"now","s":267.62,"e":267.62,"line":39}],"lines":[{"s":21.1,"e":28.4,"text":"I sent the swarm through the same tiny hands in the beam"},{"s":29.78,"e":36.24,"text":"Clockwork teeth in the haze, cut the night into days"},{"s":37.02,"e":43.5,"text":"One small spark in my palm, one long plan cold and calm"},{"s":43.68,"e":50.1,"text":"I told time hold still, then I bent it to my will"},{"s":52.1,"e":58.86,"text":"Hear that crack in the sky, that was me, that was I"},{"s":59.82,"e":66.1,"text":"Every second came undone, when the silver tide had come"},{"s":67.34,"e":72.72,"text":"Taken down, taken down, pulled across from the ground"},{"s":73.74,"e":81.56,"text":"Making king of the deep, let the old ways keep"},{"s":81.86,"e":87.58,"text":"Atlantis rise now, from the salt in the shroud"},{"s":88.98,"e":95.48,"text":"I won by the blood, I won by the blood"},{"s":97.28,"e":103.6,"text":"Little lights in the sand, took the nails from his hand"},{"s":103.72,"e":110.04,"text":"Turned the wood into gold, gave the broken a hold"},{"s":112.06,"e":117.42,"text":"Then the sea opened wide, like a mouth with a tide"},{"s":117.42,"e":124.98,"text":"And the crown in the foam, made the ruin a throne"},{"s":127.42,"e":133.4,"text":"Hear that crack in the sky, that was me, that was I"},{"s":134.52,"e":141.02,"text":"Every second came undone, when the silver tide had come"},{"s":142.02,"e":147.24,"text":"Taken down, taken down, pulled across from the ground"},{"s":148.3,"e":154.74,"text":"Making king of the deep, let the old ways keep"},{"s":156.24,"e":161.92,"text":"Atlantis rise now, from the salt in the shroud"},{"s":163.26,"e":169.34,"text":"I won by the blood, I won by the blood"},{"s":173.76,"e":174.64,"text":"OOP"},{"s":186.86,"e":190.6,"text":"Coral on the iron, stars in the brine"},{"s":190.6,"e":194.42,"text":"He walked through the blue and the future bowed in time"},{"s":194.42,"e":197.84,"text":"No more dust, no more shame"},{"s":197.84,"e":200.74,"text":"Only waves calling his name"},{"s":200.74,"e":203.74,"text":"I opened the door"},{"s":206.64,"e":212.78,"text":"And the sea made a g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g-g"},{"s":212.78,"e":215.28,"text":"Take him down, take him down, take him down"},{"s":215.28,"e":217.14,"text":"Pull the cross from the ground"},{"s":218.48,"e":220.86,"text":"Make him King of the Deep"},{"s":222.74,"e":224.5,"text":"Let the old waves keep"},{"s":226.36,"e":228.14,"text":"Atlantis rise now"},{"s":228.14,"e":231.74,"text":"Rise now, from the salt and the shroud"},{"s":231.94,"e":235.54,"text":"Rise now, I won by the blood"},{"s":236.96,"e":239.16,"text":"I won by the blood"},{"s":241.36,"e":246.44,"text":"Take him down, take him down, take him down"},{"s":247.52,"e":250.14,"text":"Now the abyss sings loud"},{"s":252.04,"e":254.48,"text":"Atlantis rise now"},{"s":255.64,"e":257.14,"text":"Atlantis rise now"},{"s":266.22,"e":267.62,"text":"Atlantis rise now"}],"duration":267.6400146484375,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:32:04.342Z","model":"whisper-1"}